{"tid":1794781,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「文宣核彈」將警員稱示威者「曱甴」　警民關係主任：從正面看富有生命力 呢單新聞推上twitter","createTime":"2019-12-23T11:24:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T07:06:53.000Z","uid":150842,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e221d3f49eaf478e1e8b7c1d365526b01c8ca3f9","tid":1794781,"uid":150842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T11:24:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NNQHkH0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNNQHkH0.jpg&h=9a22689e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n反修例運動6月爆發至觸發多場警民衝突。警察員佐級協會主席林志偉7月在聲明中曾將示威者比喻成「曱甴」，其後有警員多次在執法其間以此稱呼示威者。警隊警民關係主任譚汝禧接受港台節目《鏗鏘集》訪問時稱，市民無需對一些稱呼過分解讀，更反問「曱甴從正面去看，是否富有生命力？」<br />\n<br />\n警察公共關係科總警司郭嘉銓今日（23日）在記者會表示，未看過相關片段，但認為用任何外號或詞語標籤任何人也不理想。他又說過去半年各方也有不同情緒，警方一直有向警員進行情緒管理，希望警民關係可隨衝突減少而緩和。<br />\n<br />\n譚汝禧在訪問中表示，相信同袍的恪守專業，並履行警隊誓詞中的「不對他人懷有惡意」。不過他又認為，警隊目前的整體情緒是很失望和沮喪。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">他又指，「曱甴當然你們會認為是很差的比喻，但倒轉看，曱甴從正面去看，是否富有生命力？」</span></span>，認為市民無需就此過分演繹或解讀。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家幫幫手推呢段訪問上twitter，再tag Nazi 同盧旺達大屠殺 or chinazi，俾全世界睇香港警察點演譯cockroaches 呢隻字<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />信我，將會係核彈炸爆歐洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望大家可以自由發揮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"fe415c82ea3a364aa5414487140e35f865ebfb52","tid":1794781,"uid":150842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T11:24:35.000Z","msg":"幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2645eee98229cc139a88079c984ed20246e3744b","tid":1794781,"uid":150842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T11:24:49.000Z","msg":"文宣核彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26dfbcb9860b9f910aa4d3d437f63df987cac180","tid":1794781,"uid":150842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T11:25:00.000Z","msg":"文宣核彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd5654bcd3f036c9f290ff5639a212c6e3db9dbb","tid":1794781,"uid":150842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T11:25:17.000Z","msg":"文宣核彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />炸爆歐洲德國"},{"pid":"a8e430630fdb92291931d315b77ffb64bcd36c29","tid":1794781,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T11:25:32.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-----------------<br />\n香港獨立，唯一出路<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ba3f93a34a85080b1425d10f88d15e566de9313","tid":1794781,"uid":150842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T11:25:49.000Z","msg":"文宣核彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />炸爆歐洲德國<br />\n將黑警主義包成聖誕禮物送俾歐洲"},{"pid":"3565651d6943120dde936a289a352da31d81445b","tid":1794781,"uid":130797,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T11:25:55.000Z","msg":"推呀<br />\n公職人員鳩up係有後果"},{"pid":"9a1ac367b366685ba891998c3ae53415dc0e07ea","tid":1794781,"uid":150842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T11:25:59.000Z","msg":"文宣核彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />炸爆歐洲德國<br />\n將黑警主義包成聖誕禮物送俾歐洲"},{"pid":"564550aa44e6e38bcef7f98e542b469e58578d3a","tid":1794781,"uid":268660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T11:26:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"032acf5545dfa3e52d23e8846a7429aa1a1e18fe","tid":1794781,"uid"